  "title": "🏆 Brand Ambassador (Events) 💯",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🔥 Join Euphoria Organization — Sales & Events Role! 🔥</strong></h1><p>Looking for a fun, fast-paced career with growth? We’re hiring <strong>Sales & Marketing Executives</strong> for events, residential campaigns & roadshows! No experience needed — just great energy. 💥</p><h2><strong>✨ What You’ll Do</strong></h2><ul><li><p>🚀 Represent brands at events & roadshows</p></li><li><p>💬 Engage customers confidently</p></li><li><p>🎯 Learn & apply sales/marketing skills</p></li><li><p>🤝 Work with a dynamic, supportive team</p></li></ul><h2><strong>🌟 What You Get</strong></h2><ul><li><p>💸 <strong>Uncapped earnings</strong></p></li><li><p>🌍 Travel opportunities</p></li><li><p>🎉 Fun team culture</p></li><li><p>📚 Training & personal development</p></li><li><p>🔝 Clear progression pathway</p></li></ul><h2><strong>💡 We Want People Who Are</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Energetic, motivated & team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Enjoy talking to people 😄</p></li><li><p>Ready to learn (no experience needed!)</p></li></ul><h2><strong>📍 Join Us Today!</strong></h2><p>Start a career that grows with you. <strong>Apply now! 🚀</strong></p>",
